column2: I am 18+ and I consent to anonymous data collection for academic purposes only.
column7: Which wellness/mental health apps have you used in the last 6 months? (select all that apply)
column9: How often do you chat with an AI companion for support?
column11: How often do you journal late at night (after 11pm)?
column12: Average sleep hours per night (past 2 weeks)
column13: Average number of meetings/classes per day (past 2 weeks)
column14: How many deadlines/exams in the next 7 days?
column15: In the last 2 weeks, how often did you feel overwhelmed?
column16: In the last 2 weeks, how often did you feel things were going your way? (reverse-scored)
column17: In the last 2 weeks, how often did you feel confident about handling personal problems? (reverse-scored)
column18: In the last 2 weeks, how often did you feel difficulties were piling up too high?
column20: Which emotions did you often experience in the last week? (select all that apply)
column21: I am concerned about privacy of my journals.
column22: I prefer on-device processing even if features are limited.
column23: I am okay with personalized nudges if they help my wellbeing.
column24: I am willing to share anonymized analytics for research.
column25: What would you want from a wellbeing companion? (open text)
column26: Any concerns about such apps? (open text)
